<!--
Mods -- SpellID:Type:Value
SpellID: The spell to be affected by this Aura. -1 for all.
Type: Damage, Cost, Cooldown, Proc
Value: % change to SpellID's Type.
	Multiplication order:
		Base * buff Auras * debuff Auras
		Auras are applied in greatest-to-least order (100% increase applied before a 10%)
Split different effects with a single forward slash, i.e "1:Damage:1/2:Cost:2"
-->